<br>
Nice to know someone reads my posts :-)<br>
<br>
A little added info I did not include plus an correction.<br>
<br>
First of all exp gain plus loot.<br>
<br>
At 51 I gained half a blue bubble from a single quadkite.<br>
<br>
They drop random amounts of money, think the highest gained from one is 6pp.<br>
<br>
They drop research components for all spell classes. Lvl 39 spells I belive.<br>
<br>
They drop jewelry items. They commonly go for 10 15 pp a piece.<br>
<br>
They drop gems..... armor quest gems..... and crap gems.<br>
<br>
Crap gems goes for 46pp with the ottermen. Maybe more if you have higher charisma (92) or better faction (indifferent).<br>
<br>
Quest armor gems.<br>
In the beginning of my kiting days I exclusively got flawed gems. But with time I have gained other types. Nephrite and jaudice. I have however not received any crushed gems.<br>
<br>
Arctic wyvern skin. Velious tailoring armor component (shaman only) Got 23 in the bank. Might even give it a go if I can get my tailoring up to 150 (Trivial &gt;200).<br>
<br>
Now my correction. In my original post I wrote that the fourth hit from pillar of frost was always a partial effect. I can say that I have successfully at lvl 52 nuked 4 wyverns for full effect. So max effect on Pillar at frost (lvl 52) is.<br>
<br>
4 x 760 = 3040 points of damage. :-)<br>
<br>
9.3 points of damage per mana.<br>
Enough said.<br>
